============================================================
Опция -std=c++17 должна следовать ПЕРЕД getline.o при линковке
all ===> basic
checking C++ compiler type... gcc 10.3.1
checking for program c++... /usr/bin/c++
c++             -std=c++17   -c -o getline.o   getline.cc
c++ -o getline getline.o     -std=c++17   
c++             -std=c++17   -c -o init.o   init.cc
c++ -o init init.o     -std=c++17   

============================================================
Linker options like -Wl,-E --version-script etc.
should be checked as a part of mk-configure compilation time.
tcc, for example, does not have --version-script on gnuld
systems.

